<!-- Who I Am -->
<section id="whoiam">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="title">
      Who We <span>Are</span>
    </h1>
    <h2 class="sub-title">
      A Colombian company, with 13 years of experience in the market, that offers fresh and affordable trends for every stage of a woman.
    </h2>
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="span6 first">
        <h4 class="heading turquoise"><i class="fa fa-suitcase"></i> Our <strong>Mission</strong>  </h4>
        <p>
          We are a company committed in designing and marketing of clothing for each stage of a woman. To archive it, we are focused on transforming the product according to the demands of quality, technology and vanguard in the market, projecting us on the client as a versatile and accessible brand for modern woman.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="span6">
        <h4 class="heading blue"><i class="fa fa-eye"></i> Our <strong>Vision</strong></h4>  
        <p>
          Being a company positioned in the national and international market, focused on the production of high quality women's clothes, always in touch with new trends, fashion and standards of qualified team that evaluates the product in all its stages, to transform it into a relevant and accessible option for the modern woman.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <h3 class="heading orange"><i class="fa fa-users"></i> Our <strong>Essence</strong></h3>
    
    <div class="add-md-top">
      <p>
        We understand that every stage of your life is one step closer to your personal fulfillment, so we design each and every of our garments trying to make your life more practical and fun. You are our inspiration, and we want your image to project the versatility and femininity of being a woman.
      </p>
      <p>
        We know you are multifaceted, decisive in every moment of life, essential in your family, Determinant in the company and a key to society, so we think that the outlay you make will be the right one, where what you get means  every situation where you can develop. Your growth is part of our history, so we will always offer you fresh and authentic trends that comes in harmony with your style.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

