        <h1 class="section-title text-center" ><i class="icon-picons-home-2"></i>
        How dit it start?</h1>
        <p class="history-text">
          In 2000, Siomara sierra joins as an ideal partner to maximize a dream company of two friends, between them including her sister Lilana Sierra who was an unconditional support for the flowering and permanence of the company in its beginnings. The initial idea from the duo emerges from designing women’s clothes produced by subcontractors and sold in a personalized way all over the world; however their business idea was conceived as an uncertain and distant future.
        </p> 
        <p class="history-text">
          Although the idea worked on a small scale, and it was staying in the market, the view that Siomara Sierra had about the business was stronger, and sensed as a close reality.
        </p>
        <p class="history-text">
          <div class="phrase">
            <i class="fa fa-quote-left"></i><i> A clear and powerful idea soon becomes in a close reality </i><i class="fa fa-quote-right"></i>.
          </div>
          The hazards of life did not wait and when someone has a conviction of something doesn’t give up until they get it, with this confidence Siomara sierra raised up from various situations, to continue with her own project, where step by step , with effort and courage has seen it bearing fruits.
          <a href="#" class="read-more">Read more</a>
        </p>
        <div class="more">
          <p class="history-text">
            This is how the brand Siomara Sierra has been extended and consolidated for thirteen years in national level, as a known company in women’s confection and vanguard sector, where inputs are transformed into quality products, style and affordability, always designed to go with every women in each of her stages. 
          </p>
          <p class="history-text">
            A working structure, with performing manufacturing plants and a committed team, they are part of the garment evaluation process, which gives strong value and warranty when trading. The brand Siomara Sierra stepped to the opening of new markets on an internationally way and to the challenges imposed by the society, and it qualifies to continue growing, adding benefits to its differentiating attributes permanently.
            <a class="show-less" href="#">Close</a>
          </p>
        </div>
          
      </aside>
    </div>
